               </bibl>.</p>
            <p xml:id="footnote-2">[2]. Private collection (USA), no. 30, published in <bibl>
                  <ptr target="Nesbitt1998"/>, p. <citedRange unit="page">167-168</citedRange>, no. <citedRange unit="entry">10</citedRange>
               </bibl>.</p>
